Text:
Great music as always :)
I know I've made a request already but I have a few other bands to request!!

A Night At The Chalet
Burn My Heart At Sunset
Garden Of Stained Graves
Decades Of Deception
Murderwalk

If you could get one, just any one of thoses, it would make me a happy man :) 
Thanks again for all your great music and keep up the hard work ;)
